'''''The Day of My Wedding''''', ni filime ngufi ya [[Botswana|Botswana yo mu]] 2007 iyobowe na Thato Rantao Mwosa kandi yakozwe na Thato Rantao Mwosa nka SaBantu Productions.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Erickka Jones mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Souleymane Sy Savane na Audrey Aduama mu nshingano zunganira. 

Filime yafatiwe muri Boston no muri Massachusetts, muri [[Amerika]]. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Roxbury, muri [[Amerika]] ku ya 4 Kanama 2007.

